            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Here are some examples from users reporting ALE issues with `ch_logfile`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/w0rp/ale/issues/1918#issuecomment-423621079\r\nhttps://github.com/w0rp/ale/issues/1407#issuecomment-375119824\r\nhttps://github.com/w0rp/ale/issues/1200#issuecomment-354515628\r\nhttps://github.com/w0rp/ale/issues/1149#issuecomment-345560284\r\n\r\nThe output shows jobs starting and stopping, channels opening and closing, messages that are sent back and forth, and so on. All of the above make spotting bugs pretty easy.",
